    <abstract>
      <t>In some multihoming SRv6 L3VPN and EVPN scenarios, there are requirements for the egress PE to advertise both unicast and anycast SRv6 Service SIDs for the same service. This document defines the Anycast-flag for SRv6 Service SIDs carried in BGP messages.</t>
